In r18104 this code worked just fine:
{code}
	@BeanProperty
	@OneToMany(fetch = FetchType.EAGER, mappedBy="menu", cascade = Array(CascadeType.ALL))
	@OrderBy(value = "displayOrder ASC")
	var myList: java.util.List[Item] = _
{code}

